description: ArcGIS Runtime SDK for .NET enables you to add powerful mapping and spatial capabilities to your Universal Windows Platform (UWP) apps. Use a wide range of mapping and GIS tasks online and offline, including data visualization, editing, geocoding, and routing.
summary: ArcGIS Runtime SDK for .NET adds maps, 3D scenes, and powerful spatial capabilities to your UWP apps.
title: ArcGIS Runtime SDK for .NET - UWP
